England and Pakistan faced each other for the 4th T20I at The Oval. England showcased a brilliant performance with both bat and ball and took down Pakistan comfortably. Pakistan batted first, posted 157 runs and became all-out in the process. Later, England batters chased down the total in 15.3 overs to seal a series victory just before the T20 World Cup.

snippet.title: Praggnanandhaa stuns Magnus Carlsen | First win in Classical Chess | Norway Chess 2024
snippet.description:
Praggnanandhaa has beaten Magnus Carlsen several times before. This he managed to do in Champions Chess Tour in 2022. Recently at the Superbet Grand Chess Tour in Warsaw he beat Magnus for the first time in over the board chess, but that Blitz. Pragg had never beaten Carlsen in classical format. This he managed to do on 30th May 2024 at the 3rd round of the Norway Chess 2024. A fantastic game with tremendous accuracy. Check out this battle between the World no.1 and the rising star of Indian chess with commentary by IM Sagar Shah.

snippet.description:
Aloo Naan Recipe #aloonaan #naan  Super Soft Aloo Naan Roti on Tawa. This Video show How to make fluffy soft potato naan roti or aloo naan recipe at home. We make easily aloo naan at home on tawa. The easiest way to make Aloo Naan just like Dhaba. No flour, no tandoor, make Atta Potato Naan in 10 minutes like this is a Instant Dhaba Style Aalu Butter Naan Recipe.  Potato Naan is made by preparing the dough: Mixing flour, yeast, salt, baking soda, baking powder and plain yogurt or buttermilk.

#naanrecipe #naanrecipes #aloonaankirecipe #stuffednaan #kulcha #alookulcha 
#cookwithparul  #cookwithparulrecipe 
https://www.youtube.com/CookWithParul/
https://www.instagram.com/cookwithparul/
https://www.facebook.com/CookwithParulGupta 
https://www.instagram.com/chef_parulgupta/

Ingredients List:
All Purpose Flour - 500 gm
Nigella - 1tsp
Salt - 1 tsp
Baking Powder - 1 tsp
Pure Ghee - 2 tbsp 
Chopped Coriander
Boiled Potato - 4
Curd - 1/2 cup
Milk - 2 tbsp
Oil- 1 tsp
Butter - 2 tbsp
Garlic - 2 tbsp
Chopped Coriander

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: 2nd T20I | Highlights | Pakistan Tour Of England | 25th May 2024
snippet.description:
In the 2nd T20I of the Pakistan Tour Of England, the hosts set a target of 183, with Jos Buttler's scintillating 84 runs off 51 balls leading the charge. Shaheen Afridi's impressive bowling, with 3 wickets at an economy of 9, kept Pakistan in the contest. However, England's bowlers, spearheaded by Reece Topley who also claimed 3 wickets, managed to restrict Pakistan to 160 runs. Despite Fakhar Zaman's explosive 45 runs off 21 balls, Pakistan fell short by 23 runs.
